    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single gap in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is acknowledged; the single-condition F1717 protocol is consistent with regulatory practice and the gap does not invalidate the overall assessment given the strength of evidence across remaining factors. Experimental evidence from N=11 constructs across two laboratories corroborates the FEA predictions. The summary accuracy claim is considered supported by the body of validation work described in this package.",
